Richard Tyson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Tyson 0 Richard Martin Tyson is an American actor. Tyson was born in Mobile, Alabama. Tyson is a member of the Shriners. His brother John is the former District Attorney of Mobile County and was the Democratic Party nominee for Attorney General of Alabama in 2006. Richard_Martin_Tyson is an_American_actor .
